{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was offered a position\nas associate professor of medicine"},{"time":3738,"text":"and chief of scientific visualization"},{"time":6570,"text":"at Yale University"},{"time":8571,"text":"in the department of medicine."},{"time":10204,"text":"And my job was to write\nmany of the algorithms and code"},{"time":13000,"text":"for NASA to do virtual surgery"},{"time":15000,"text":"in preparation for the astronauts\ngoing into deep-space flight,"},{"time":18000,"text":"so they could be kept in robotic pods."},{"time":20000,"text":"One of the fascinating things\nabout what we were working on"},{"time":22930,"text":"is that we were seeing,\nusing new scanning technologies,"},{"time":25972,"text":"things that had never been seen before."},{"time":27977,"text":"Not only in disease management,"},{"time":29575,"text":"but also things that allowed us\nto see things about the body"},{"time":33000,"text":"that just made you marvel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"I remember one of the first times\nwe were looking at collagen."},{"time":39000,"text":"And your entire body, everything --"},{"time":41000,"text":"your hair, skin, bone, nails --"},{"time":43000,"text":"everything is made of collagen."},{"time":45000,"text":"And it's a kind of rope-like structure\nthat twirls and swirls like this."},{"time":49952,"text":"And the only place that collagen\nchanges its structure"},{"time":54181,"text":"is in the cornea of your eye."},{"time":55981,"text":"In your eye,\nit becomes a grid formation,"},{"time":59380,"text":"and therefore, it becomes\ntransparent, as opposed to opaque."},{"time":62711,"text":"So perfectly organized a structure,"},{"time":65000,"text":"it was hard not to attribute\ndivinity to it."},{"time":67538,"text":"Because we kept on seeing this\nin different parts of the body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72660,"text":"One of the opportunities I had"},{"time":75000,"text":"was one person was working\non a really interesting"},{"time":77405,"text":"micromagnetic resonance\nimaging machine with the NIH."},{"time":80000,"text":"And what we were going to do"},{"time":82000,"text":"was scan a new project"},{"time":84000,"text":"on the development of the fetus\nfrom conception to birth"},{"time":86854,"text":"using these new technologies."},{"time":88552,"text":"So I wrote the algorithms and code,"},{"time":90533,"text":"and he built the hardware --\nPaul Lauterbur --"},{"time":93000,"text":"then went onto win the Nobel\nPrize for inventing the MRI."},{"time":96557,"text":"I got the data."},{"time":98000,"text":"And I'm going to show you\na sample of the piece,"},{"time":100684,"text":"\"From Conception to Birth.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":102281,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107467,"text":"[From Conception to Birth]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":113784,"text":"[Oocyte]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119000,"text":"[Sperm]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"[Egg Inseminated]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132396,"text":"[24 Hours: Baby's first division]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"[The fertilized ovum divides\na few hours after fusion...]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"[And divides anew every 12 to 15 hours.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146852,"text":"[Early Embryo]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149895,"text":"[Yolk sack still feeding baby.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"[25 Days: Heart chamber developing.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160784,"text":"[32 Days: Arms &amp; hands are developing]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170408,"text":"[36 Days: Beginning\nof the primitive vertebrae]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"[These weeks are the period\nof the most rapid development"},{"time":180294,"text":"of the fetus.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"[If the fetus continues to grow\nat this speed for the entire 9 months,"},{"time":192453,"text":"it would be 1.5 tons at birth.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"[45 Days]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204816,"text":"[Embryo's heart is beating\ntwice as fast as the mother's.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":211000,"text":"[51 Days]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":214000,"text":"[Developing retina, nose and fingers]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228757,"text":"[The fetus' continual movement in the womb"},{"time":233000,"text":"is necessary for muscular\nand skeletal growth.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"[12 Weeks: Indifferent penis]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"[Girl or boy yet to be determined]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256680,"text":"[8 Months]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"[Delivery: The expulsion stage]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":328135,"text":"[The moment of birth]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":338247,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341841,"text":"Alexander Tsiaras: Thank you."},{"time":344265,"text":"But as you can see,"},{"time":345566,"text":"when you actually start\nworking on this data,"},{"time":347767,"text":"it's pretty spectacular."},{"time":349000,"text":"And as we kept on scanning more and more,"},{"time":351639,"text":"working on this project,"},{"time":353858,"text":"looking at these two simple cells"},{"time":355953,"text":"that have this unbelievable machinery\nthat will become the magic of you."},{"time":360000,"text":"And as we kept on working on this data,"},{"time":362000,"text":"looking at small clusters of the body,"},{"time":365000,"text":"these little pieces of tissue"},{"time":368000,"text":"that were the trophoblasts\ncoming off of the blastocyst,"},{"time":370956,"text":"all of a sudden burrowing itself\ninto the side of the uterus,"},{"time":373942,"text":"saying, \"I'm here to stay.\""},{"time":375300,"text":"Having conversation and communications"},{"time":377200,"text":"with the estrogens, the progesterones,"},{"time":379100,"text":"saying, \"I'm here to stay, plant me,\""},{"time":381780,"text":"building this incredible trilinear fetus"},{"time":385090,"text":"that becomes, within 44 days,\nsomething that you can recognize,"},{"time":388200,"text":"and then at nine weeks\nis really kind of a little human being."},{"time":392000,"text":"The marvel of this information:"},{"time":394000,"text":"How do we actually have\nthis biological mechanism"},{"time":397392,"text":"inside our body"},{"time":398716,"text":"to actually see this information?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400629,"text":"I'm going to show you\nsomething pretty unique."},{"time":402940,"text":"Here's a human heart at 25 days."},{"time":404957,"text":"It's just basically two strands."},{"time":406574,"text":"And like this magnificent origami,"},{"time":408300,"text":"cells are developing at one million cells\nper second at four weeks,"},{"time":413000,"text":"as it's just folding on itself."},{"time":415000,"text":"Within five weeks, you start to see\nthe early atrium and the early ventricles."},{"time":418805,"text":"Six weeks, these folds are now beginning"},{"time":421049,"text":"with the papilla\non the inside of the heart"},{"time":423230,"text":"actually being able to pull down\neach one of those valves in your heart"},{"time":426700,"text":"until you get a mature heart --"},{"time":429000,"text":"and then basically the development\nof the entire human body."},{"time":431913,"text":"The magic of the mechanisms\ninside each genetic structure"},{"time":436000,"text":"saying exactly where\nthat nerve cell should go --"},{"time":439000,"text":"the complexity of these,"},{"time":441030,"text":"the mathematical models\nof how these things are indeed done"},{"time":443951,"text":"are beyond human comprehension."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445846,"text":"Even though I am a mathematician,"},{"time":447793,"text":"I look at this with marvel"},{"time":449732,"text":"of how do these instruction sets\nnot make these mistakes"},{"time":454000,"text":"as they build what is us?"},{"time":456000,"text":"It's a mystery, it's magic, it's divinity."},{"time":458024,"text":"Then you start to take\na look at adult life."},{"time":461000,"text":"Take a look at this\nlittle tuft of capillaries."},{"time":463263,"text":"It's just a tiny\nsub-substructure, microscopic."},{"time":466000,"text":"But basically by the time you're\nnine months and you're given birth,"},{"time":470671,"text":"you have almost 60,000 miles\nof vessels inside your body."},{"time":475317,"text":"And only one mile is visible."},{"time":477468,"text":"59,999 miles"},{"time":480000,"text":"that are basically bringing\nnutrients and taking waste away."},{"time":483000,"text":"The complexity of building\nthat within a single system"},{"time":485685,"text":"is, again, beyond any comprehension\nor any existing mathematics today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489594,"text":"And then instructions set,"},{"time":491000,"text":"from the brain to every other\npart of the body --"},{"time":493809,"text":"look at the complexity of the folding."},{"time":495687,"text":"Where does this intelligence"},{"time":497100,"text":"of knowing that a fold can\nactually hold more information,"},{"time":499939,"text":"so as you actually watch\nthe baby's brain grow."},{"time":502555,"text":"And this is one of the things we're doing."},{"time":504723,"text":"We're launching two new studies"},{"time":506300,"text":"of scanning babies' brains\nfrom the moment they're born."},{"time":509097,"text":"Every six months\nuntil they're six years old,"},{"time":511312,"text":"we're going to be doing\nabout 250 children,"},{"time":514000,"text":"watching exactly how the gyri\nand the sulci of the brains fold"},{"time":517727,"text":"to see how this magnificent development"},{"time":519788,"text":"actually turns into memories\nand the marvel that is us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522400,"text":"And it's not just our own existence,"},{"time":524200,"text":"but how does the woman's body understand"},{"time":527066,"text":"to have genetic structure\nthat not only builds her own,"},{"time":529771,"text":"but then has the understanding"},{"time":531300,"text":"that allows her to become"},{"time":533000,"text":"a walking immunological,\ncardiovascular system"},{"time":536000,"text":"that basically is a mobile system"},{"time":538000,"text":"that can actually nurture,"},{"time":539859,"text":"treat this child with a kind of marvel"},{"time":542000,"text":"that is beyond, again,\nour comprehension --"},{"time":545829,"text":"the magic that is existence, that is us?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":549038,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}